glosses.gloss: Finnish architect and designer of furniture (1898-1976)
Hugo Alvar Henrik Aalto was a Finnish architect and designer.
Aalto is a surname originating in Finland.
Hugo Alvar Henrik Aalto was a Finnish architect and designer, as well as a sculptor and painter.
